    "SLPs in administrative roles oversee programs, staff, budgets, and operational strategy.",
    "AI tools can streamline many time-intensive tasks such as scheduling, billing, compliance tracking, and service documentation, freeing leaders to focus on higher-level planning.",
    "Predictive analytics can also inform staffing, budgeting, and resource allocation to improve cost-effectiveness.",
    "Clinics and universities, regardless of size, may benefit from using tabular AI models to analyze financial data and optimize workflows.",
